com.baypackets.ase.sbb
Interface SBBCallback

All Known Subinterfaces:
EarlyMediaCallback
public interface SBBCallback

The SBB Callback interface. This is the base class for all the callback interfaces. The Callback interfaces are used by the applications to provide a callbacks to the SBB asynchronously. The application uses the callbacks to notify the SBB objects with current state of a specific operations. The callback objects can be obtained from the SBB using the getCallback() method.
